OL,3,C'More time needed' to achieve 'best
OL,4,Cversion' of Hillsborough law
OL,6,FMore time is needed to achieve the
OL,7,F"best version" of a Hillsborough law,
OL,8,FDowning Street has said.
OL,10,FSir Keir Starmer had pledged to
OL,11,Fintroduce a bill, placing a legal duty
OL,12,Fof candour on public authorities
OL,13,Fbefore the tragedy's 36th anniversary
OL,14,Fon Tuesday, 15 April.
OL,16,FBut when asked whether the promise
OL,17,Fwill be delivered, a spokesperson for
OL,18,Fthe Prime Minister said the government
OL,19,Fwould need more time, adding that they
OL,20,F"remain fully committed to bringing
OL,21,Fthis legislation in at pace".
