OL,6,FSpeaking to reporters he said: "The
OL,7,FHillsborough disaster will always
OL,8,Fremain one of the greatest stains on
OL,9,Fthe history of this country.
OL,11,F"Ahead of the 36th anniversary, we pay
OL,12,Ftribute to those who lost their lives
OL,13,Fand to the families and campaigners
OL,14,Fwho have showed endless determination
OL,15,Fto get justice.
